Detailed Description

This module contains a description of the CellML Application Programming Interface in the language-neutral IDL form.

Typedef Documentation

typedef wstring cellml_api::CellMLAttributeString

This holds attribute values for the XML attributes of elements in serialised CellML. Character data in XML can be any Unicode character; the sequence of characters must conform to the rules of XML character data (which define escaping of reserved characters etc).

See also:
http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml/#syntax

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum cellml_api::VariableInterface

An enumeration representing the direction of the variable interface.

Enumerator:
INTERFACE_IN  The interface is in.
INTERFACE_OUT  The interface is out.
INTERFACE_NONE  No interface is defined.
